<i>noun</i>: 사복 [사복] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사복 [사복]</dt><br>
<dd>1. plain clothes; civilian clothes</dd><br>
<dd>제복이 아닌 평상시에 입는 보통 옷.</dd><br>
<dd>Ordinary clothes that a person normally wears, not uniform.</dd><br>
<dd>2. plainclothesman</dd><br>
<dd>범죄 수사나 잠복, 미행 등을 할 때 신분을 숨기기 위하여 제복이 아닌 평상복을 입고 근무하는 경찰.</dd><br>
<dd>A police officer who wears plain clothes, not a uniform, to work in order to conceal his/her identity during a crime investigation, stakeout, tailing, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>